# CODEOWNERS — who is auto-requested to review a PR that touches matching paths.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners
#
# Solo today, so this is intentionally a template (all lines commented = no required
# owners, no false "unknown owner" warnings). When you add developers:
#   1. set your team's GitHub handles below,
#   2. turn on "Require review from Code Owners" in the `main` branch ruleset,
#   3. bump required approvals to >= 1.
#
# Everything:
# *                       @your-github-username
#
# Examples for when the team grows:
# /supabase/migrations/   @your-db-owner
# /docs/                  @your-docs-owner
# /lib/ai/                @your-ai-owner
